Introduction

Jeong Yoonchae is a South Korean singer and dancer under Geffen Records and HYBE Labels. She is best known as the maknae of the global girl group KATSEYE.

Yoonchae is recognized for her participation in the survival show "The Debut: Dream Academy", where she ranked 3rd and qualified for debut, becoming a member of the girl group KATSEYE.

On August 16, 2024, Yoonchae officially debuted as a member of KATSEYE with their first EP "SIS (SOFT IS STRONG)".
